item.title: CVE-2017-9634|2024-08-05T17:11:02.366Z -- mitsubishi%20electric%20europe%20b.v. -- e-designer
item.description: Mitsubishi E-Designer, Version 7.52 Build 344 contains two code sections which may be exploited to allow an attacker to overwrite arbitrary memory locations. This can result in arbitrary code execution, compromised data integrity, denial of service, and system crash.
